{"tid":1538411,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[對準春袋]証明渣機場春袋真係好緊要","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:17:06.000Z","uid":65790,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fa17fb59d7cabbc0958fdd2daa179af664519d94","tid":1538411,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:00:39.000Z","msg":"上星期日渣完機場春袋即刻點應左其中一個訴求<br />\n今個星期六(7/9)繼續渣, 渣多四個星期大家就贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求,缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"13e223785495a321c501a37b8e87276b1b773b7c","tid":1538411,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"［幫手推］隔離熱門po話撤回條例會令下次遊行失去一大班和理非喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538366</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61c4bdaf76f6fc3679d12cce8f93910f926c9605","tid":1538411,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcMrUP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcMrUP7.jpg&h=f6662391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe998429d1d4fe1c1b895981865ae19728ea9f99","tid":1538411,"uid":193032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"有關破壞<br />\n<br />\n公物係用公帑，叫工人整。圍差館係送上門比差人除暴安良。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好學惡霸美國，搞阻礙香港民主進程官員嘅財產！<br />\n<br />\n勇武千祈唔好破壞私物！特別係某啲人嘅私物，財產，公司，物業。人地仲要claim保險點告到你班仆街暴動！<br />\n<br />\n和理非千祈唔好係唔犯法嘅情況令啲嘢貶值，例如唔小心跌左啲好臭嘅嘢，識郁嘅嘢。黑材料，桃色糾紛乜乜乜啊。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好！<br />\n<br />\n特別係唔好hit and run! 好衰！"},{"pid":"81f8cb6e389348999851099b4860490fcebe607d","tid":1538411,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime